#variable which store the value  . variable is a container used to store data values during program execution. Variable  have two type local ,static , instance variable 
  local variable : decarlare inside a method , construtor or block .
  instance variable decalred inside a class but outside methods 
    static vsriable declared using the static key word (Static variable sab objects ke liye ek hi hota hai).
    


